description: A lot of the gay solos that come in always have a SeanCody favorite that they hope to one day get paired with. For Manny it was hands down Tanner. “There is just something about him, I cant put my finger on it. I think maybe cause I’ve see him do some pretty dirty things on the site, it’s a huge turn on." Tanner had a devilish look in his eye. “Oh I have some things planned for sure! Tanner didn’t disappoint either, by the time Manny left the SeanCody studios he could barely walk but he did have a smile ear to ear and a nice full load of Tanner inside of him.
title: Manny & Tanner: Bareback
